snippet.title: Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2 - Official Mr. Krabs Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2 is a platform fighter developed by Fair Play Labs and Ludosity. Bikini Bottom's favorite business owner Mr. Krabs has joined the fight. Take a look at the latest trailer to get a feel for his moveset and gameplay mechanics. Mr. Krabs comes to Nickelodeon All-Star Brawl 2 on February 15 for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#IGN #Gaming #MrKrabs #NickelodeonAllStarBrawl2
